    "htmlContent": "<h2>Core Playbook</h2>\n<p>Pharah uses Jump Jet and Hover to stay airborne out of melee range, raining down Rocket Launcher splash damage on grouped enemies below.</p>\n<h2>Tactical Caveats</h2>\n<p>She's highly visible and has a large hurtbox in the air, making her one of the most reliable targets for a dedicated hitscan hero like Ashe or Soldier: 76 to shoot down.</p>"
